parse.title: List of towns and cities with 100,000 or more inhabitants/country: T-U-V-W

text.*:
This is a list of towns and cities in the world in alphabetical order, beginning with the letters T, U, V and W, by country believed to have 100,000 or more inhabitants. Unless otherwise noted, populations are based on 2009 United Nations estimates.
